  <title translate="true">MT-POP-Counts</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Motion<keyword translate="true">What are Counts</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="width:450px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Parameter" style="font-size:9pt;" translate="true">Counts</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="Parameter" style="font-size:9pt;" translate="true">Count/Unit </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">: a unit that you can apply to the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">X–axis</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Y–axis</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">. Frequently, used to design a motion for a servo-motor. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">E.g.: a Servo-motor pacer-encoder (master) has 4096 </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">counts</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> per rotation. and the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" style="font-size:9pt;" translate="true">Count/unit</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> can be set to 4096/360.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small"><text styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Edit-Active-Motion-Settings" anchor="Motion" styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">Active Motion Settings &gt; Motion tab &gt; Motion Units</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
